title: Cops probing presence of minors at Act 355 rally
text:
More 
Initial investigations by the police have uncovered that infants and children were at PAS' rally at Padang Merbok, Kuala Lumpur yesterday. 
According to Dang Wangi district police chief Mohd Sukri Kaman, the children were between 7 months to 15 years of age.
